title: Nice 4 bedrooms single family home in SJ Blossom Valley
posting_body: ['- Address: 298 Coty Way, San Jose 95136', '- Please ONLY drive by as existing tenants still in the house.', 'Will show by appointment only.', '- Beautiful single story home nested in quiet and nice Blossom Valley Neighborhood.', '- Centrally located, quick access to Highway 85, 87 and 101.', 'Short walk to Parkview Elementary school.', 'Park and greenbelt is only few houses away.', '- Tenants can use nice neighborhood swimming pools, HOA fee paid by owner.', '- 4 bedrooms and 2 full bath single family home', '- Gracious and open floor plan with ample light and excellent flow in kitchen, dining and living room area.', 'High ceiling in family room.', '- Updated kitchen with large 8 feet center Island, recessed lighting, designer tiles, new dish washer/range hood.', '- Hardwood flooring throughout', '- Tiles in both bathrooms', '- Dual pane windows', '- Good size 2 car garage with shelves', '- Low maintenance yards with min water requirement plants.', '- House available to see by appointment only (call Ken', 'show contact info', 'for appointment).', 'Terms & Conditions of Lease:', '- Rent is $3950 per month', '- Available to move in by 10/8/2022, Min one year lease', '- Security deposit is one month rent', '- Tenants pay for all utilities.', "- Deposit and first month's rent due at lease contract signing.", '- No pet,', 'No smoking', "- Hurry, it won't last long!", 'If interested, please call Ken', 'show contact info']
